ers%20and%20national%20chains%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20single-screen%20associations%2C%20ensures%20the%20teaser%20will%20be%20showcased%20before%20the%20film%20or%20during%20the%20interval.%20Adding%20to%20the%20anticipation%2C%20a%20supernatural%20thriller%2C%20'Shaitaan'%20plans%20to%20captivate%20audiences%20with%20its%20first%20teaser.%20Described%20as%20a%20tight%20and%20spooky%20cut%20with%20shock%20elements%2C%20the%20makers%20aim%20to%20reach%20a%20wide%20audience.%20The%20theatrical%20experience%20for%20the%20'Shaitaan'%20teaser%20begins%20on%20January%2025%2C%20while%20a%20digital%20launch%20is%20scheduled%20soon.%20Get%20ready%20for%20a%20cinematic%20feast%20with%20back-to-back%20teasers%20and%20the%20grand%20arrival%20of%20'Fighter'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Ayodhya's%20Ram%20Temple%20Looks%20From%20Space.%20See%20Pics%20By%20India's%20Satellites%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20grand%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20has%20given%20the%20country%20the%20first%20'darshan'%20or%20glimpse%20of%20the%20magnificent%20Ram%20Temple%20as%20seen%20from%20space%20using%20our%20own%20indigenous%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202.7-acre%20Ram%20Temple%20site%20can%20be%20seen%20and%20an%20enlarged%20view%20of%20the%20same%20is%20also%20provided%20using%20the%20Indian%20Remote%20Sensing%20series%20of%20satellites.%20The%20under%20construction%20temple%20was%20captured%20on%20December%2016%20last%20year%2C%20just%20about%20a%20month%20ago.%20Since%20then%2C%20dense%20fog%20over%20Ayodhya%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20clear%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ffe7ljnp8_ram-temple_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20satellite%20images%2C%20Dashrath%20Mahal%20and%20Sarayu%20River%20are%20clearly%20seen.%20The%20newly%20renovated%20Ayodhya%20railway%20station%20is%20also%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fr8q3e1a_ram-temple_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20currently%20has%20over%2050%20satellites%20in%20space%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20have%20a%20resolution%20of%20less%20than%20a%20metre.%20The%20image%20has%20been%20processed%20by%20the%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20space%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fvgodn3gg_ram-temple_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20technologies%20have%20also%20been%20used%20at%20other%20stages%20of%20the%20temple's%20construction.%20A%20big%20challenge%20in%20the%20grand%20project%20was%20to%20identify%20the%20exact%20location%20to%20place%20the%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%20The%20trust%20entrusted%20with%20building%20the%20temple%20wanted%20the%20idol%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20a%203%20feet%20X%206%20feet%20space%20where%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlok%20Sharma%2C%20International%20working%20President%20of%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20is%20closely%20involved%20with%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20project.%20He%20told%20NDTV%20that%20following%20the%20demolition%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992%2C%2040%20feet%20of%20debris%20covered%20the%20spot%20where%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20born.%20This%20debris%20had%20to%20be%20removed%20and%20the%20location%20secured%20so%20that%20the%20new%20idol%20is%20exactly%20and%20precisely%20at%20that%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20easier%20said%20than%20done%20because%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20began%20nearly%20three%20decades%20after%20the%20demolition.%20Then%2C%20space%20technology%20came%20to%20the%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20identify%20the%20exact%20spot%2C%20contractors%20for%20construction%20firm%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20used%20the%20most%20sophisticated%20Differential%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20(GPS)-based%20co-ordinates.%20The%20co-ordinates%2C%20precise%20to%20nearly%201-3%20centimetres%2C%20were%20drawn%20up.%20They%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20placement%20of%20the%20statue%20in%20the%20temple's%20garba%20griha%20or%20sanctum%20sanctorum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20precision%20equipment%20used%20in%20these%20geographical%20instruments%20also%20incorporates%20precise%20location%20signals%20from%20India's%20own%20'swadeshi%20GPS'%20--%20the%20ISRO-made%20'Navigation%20with%20Indian%20Constellation'%20or%20the%20NavIC%20satellite%20constellation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20chairman%20S%20Somanath%20told%20NDTV%20that%20five%20satellites%20of%20the%20NAvIC%20constellation%20are%20working%2C%20and%20the%20system%20is%20currently%20set%20for%20an%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705815060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Frbvs03gg_ram-temple-ani_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-temple-pran-pratistha-isro-a-view-of-ram-temple-from-space-courtesy-indias-swadeshi-satellites-4902766%22%2C%22summa