ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fus%2Fgoogle-engineer-found-spattered-blood-following-alleged-murder-wife-upscale-california-home-police%5C%22%3EFox%20News%20Digital%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Chen%20and%20Xuanyi%20Yu%20were%20employees%20at%20the%20tech%20giant%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20attorney's%20office%20said%20Chen%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20murder%20and%20faces%20prison%20if%20convicted.%20He%20is%20currently%20in%20hospital%20and%20could%20not%20be%20produced%20in%20court%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20police%20received%20a%20call%20from%20an%20acquaintance%20of%20Chen%20on%20Tuesday.%20When%20the%20cops%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%20the%20acquaintance%20told%20them%20that%20Chen%20was%20not%20answering%20his%20phone%20or%20the%20door.%20He%20said%20he%20could%20see%20Chen%20inside%20and%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bmotionless%20on%20his%20knees%2C%20had%20his%20hands%20in%20the%20air%20and%20was%20staring%20blankly%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officers%20managed%20to%20enter%20the%20house%20and%20took%20Chen%20into%20custody.%20They%20found%20his%20wife's%20body%20in%20the%20bedroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20LinkedIn%20profile%20of%20Liren%20Chen%2C%20he%20has%20been%20working%20with%20Google%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20since%20March%202020.%20He%20has%20been%20working%20on%20an%20algorithm%20for%20YouTube%20Shorts%20recommendation%2C%20according%20to%20the%20profile.%20Xuanyi%20Yu's%20LinkedIn%20profile%20states%20that%20she%20joined%20Google%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%202021.%20Earlier%2C%20she%20had%20been%20working%20at%20Amazon.%20Both%20Liren%20Chen%20and%20Xuanyi%20Yu%20are%20alumni%20of%20a%20Beijing%20university%2C%20their%20profiles%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705814400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fdrt9mlpg_liren-chen_625x300_21_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw