3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20night%2C%20Trump%20is%20at%20a%20rally...and%20he's%20going%20on%20and%20on%2C%20mentioning%20me%20multiple%20times%20as%20to%20why%20I%20didn't%20take%20security%20during%20the%20Capitol%20riots%2C%20why%20I%20didn't%20handle%20January%206%20better.%20I%20wasn't%20even%20in%20DC%20on%20January%206.%20I%20wasn't%20in%20office%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Haley%20has%20avoided%20direct%20attacks%20on%20Trump%20but%20as%20the%20election%20race%20heats%20up%2C%20she%20has%20taken%20on%20a%20more%20aggressive%20approach%20to%20Trump's%20criticisms%20of%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EToo%20old%20to%20be%20President%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Republicans%20have%20long%20used%20US%20president%20Joe%20Biden's%20old%20age%20to%20attack%20the%20Democrats%20and%20label%20him%20incapable%20of%20handling%20the%20top%20post%2C%20Haley%20has%20now%20trained%20her%20guns%20at%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20we%20really%20want%20to%20have%20two%2080-year-olds%20running%20for%20president%2C%20when%20we've%20got%20a%20country%20in%20disarray%20and%20a%20world%20on%20fire%3F%26quot%3B%20the%2052-year-old%20said%20at%20a%20recent%20public%20meeting%20in%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20the%20second%20state%20after%20Iowa%20to%20cast%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BHe%20feels%20threatened%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump%20has%20dismissed%20Haley's%20chances%20to%20defeat%20him%20in%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20former%20US%20president%20has%20launched%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20his%20former%20ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Trump%20hit%20out%20at%20Haley's%20Indian%20heritage%2C%20misspelling%20her%20first%20name%20%26quot%3BNimarata%26quot%3B%20as%20%26quot%3BNimrada%26quot%3B.%20Born%20to%20Indian%20immigrant%20parents%2C%20Haley%20was%20named%20Nimarata%20'Nikki'%20Randhawa%20and%20goes%20by%20her%20middle%20name.%20She%20changed%20her%20surname%20after%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20President%20Trump%20well.%20That's%20what%20he%20does%20when%20he%20feels%20threatened.%20I%20don't%20take%20these%20things%20personally%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Guardian%20quoted%20Haley.%20Haley's%20campaign%20manager%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20Trump's%20recent%20spate%20of%20insults%20as%20%26quot%3Btemper%20tantrums%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BLove%20letters%26quot%3B%20to%20dictators%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20also%20targeted%20Donald%20Trump's%20relationships%20with%20strongmen%20like%20China's%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20North%20Korea's%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20and%20Russia's%20Vladimir%20Putin%20--%20all%20leaders%20who%20have%20earned%20praises%20from%20the%20twice-impeached%20US%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20praised%20Xi%20a%20dozen%20time%20after%20China%20gave%20us%20Covid.%20I%20was%20tougher%20on%20China%20and%20Russia%20than%20Trump%20ever%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Reuters%20report%2C%20her%20campaign%20released%20a%20TV%20ad%20featuring%20the%20mother%20of%20a%20US%20student%20who%20died%20in%202017%20after%20being%20held%20in%20North%20Korean%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20accused%20Trump%20of%20writing%20%E2%80%9Clove%20letters%E2%80%9D%20to%20Kim%20after%20the%20student%20was%20recovered.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20obsessed%20with%20these%20dictators%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705811580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fum2557sg_trump-nikki-haley_625x300_21_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fas-us-presidential-race-heats-up-nikki-haley-targets-rival-trump-4902778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-American%20presidential%20candidate%20Nikki%20Haley%20has%20sharpened%20her%20attacks%20on%20Republican%20rival%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20her%20campaign%20