odhya%20is%20all%20set%20to%20take%20place%20on%20January%2022.%C2%A0The%20ceremony%20will%20begin%20at%2012%3A20%20pm%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20end%20by%201%20pm%2C%C2%A0though%20the%20celebrations%20will%20begin%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Temple%20will%20be%20inaugurated%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20other%20dignitaries%20including%20UP%20CM%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20UP%20Governor%20Anandiben%20Patel%2C%20and%20president%20of%20the%20temple%20trust%20Mahant%20Nritya%20Gopal%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20offices%2C%20boards%2C%20and%20corporations%20in%20several%20states%20have%20declared%20a%20half%20day%20or%20a%20holiday%20on%20January%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESignificance%20of%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20temple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20mandir%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20pilgrimage%20sites%20for%20Hindus.%20Ayodhya%20is%20considered%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20so%2C%20is%20considered%20a%20sacred%20place.%20The%20foundation%20stone%20for%20the%20Ram%20mandir%20was%20laid%20on%20August%205%2C%202020%2C%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20created%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrafted%20by%20sculptor%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20'Ram%20Lalla'%20idol%20stands%20at%2051%20inches%20and%20weighs%201.5%20tonnes.%20The%20depiction%20showcases%20Lord%20Ram%20as%20a%20five-year-old%20child%20standing%20on%20a%20lotus%20made%20from%20the%20same%20stone.%C2%A0The%20complete%20look%20of%20the%20idol%20was%20unveiled%20on%20Friday%20which%20showed%20the%20deity's%20face%20as%20well%20as%20a%20golden%20bow%20and%20arrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20oversees%20the%20Ram%20temple%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20is%20managed%20by%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra.%20The%20trust%2C%20created%20by%20the%20central%20government%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20is%20also%20overseeing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20which%20has%20an%20area%20of%202.7%20acres%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%20The%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20was%20undertaken%20by%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0with%20the%20technical%20assistance%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrities%20invited%20to%C2%A0Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%207%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20invited%20by%20the%20temple%20trust%2C%20and%20they%20include%20cricket%20legends%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20Bollywood%20superstars%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Rajnikant%2C%20Anushka%20Sharma%2C%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20and%20industrialists%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvitations%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20Infosys%20founder%20NR%20Narayana%20Murthy%20and%20his%20wife%20and%20author%20Sudha%20Murty%2C%20S%20N%20Subrahmanyan%20of%20the%20L%26amp%3BT%20Group%2C%20Olympic%20gold%20medallist%20Neeraj%20Chopra%2C%20Olympic%20silver%20medallist%20PV%20Sindhu%20and%20former%20cricketer%20Venkatesh%20Prasad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDarshan%20timings%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Mandir%20will%20be%20open%20for%20devotees%20from%20January%2023.%20The%20darshan%20timings%20are%20divided%20into%20two%20slots%20--%20from%207%20am%20to%2011.30%20am%20and%202%20pm%20to%207%20pm.%20To%20attend%20the%20aarti%2C%20individuals%20need%20a%20pass%20issued%20by%20the%20trust%2C%20for%20which%20a%20valid%20ID%20proof%20must%20be%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20reach%20Ram%20Mandir%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20can%20be%20reached%20by%20road%2C%20railway%2C%20or%20by%20air.%C2%A0The%20Maharishi%20Valmiki%20Airport%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20recently%20been%20inaugurated%20connecting%20the%20temple%20city%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20also%20inaugurated%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20from%20Ayodhya%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20public%20and%20private%20service%20buses%20that%20operate%20regularly%20to%20Ayodhya%20are%20available.%20Buses%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20other%20major%20cities%20are%20provided%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Transport%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%20of%20Ram%20temple%20construction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20had%20estimated%20in%202022%20that%20%E2%82%B9%201%2C800%20crore%20will%20be%20spent%20in%20building%20the%20grand%20Ram%20temple.%20In%20October%20last%20year%2C%20a%20PTI%20report%20said%20that%20the%20trust%20spent%20%E2%82%B9%20900%20crore%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20between%20February%205%2C%202020%20and%20March%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20people%20can%20also%20watch%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-temple-event-schedule-guest-list-and-other-things-you-need-to-know-4884508%5C%22%3ERam%20Mandir%20inauguration%20online%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Viewers%20can%20log%20on%20to%20NDTV's%20website%20and%20social%20media%20handles%20to%20virtually%20take%20part%20in%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony.%20Users%20can%20click%20on%20ndtv.com%2Flive.%20The%20updates%20will%20also%20be%20provided%20on%20NDTV%20live%20blog.%20The%20event%20will%20also%20be%20streamed%20live%20on%20NDTV's%20regional%20websites%2C%20as%20well%20as%20NDTV%20India%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705809780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ffnsoao1o_ram-m