3EPolitical%20scientists%20view%20the%20broadsides%20as%20an%20increasingly%20desperate%20tactic%20by%20a%20government%20that%20is%20running%20out%20of%20ideas%20and%20probably%20in%20its%20death%20throes%2C%20after%2014%20years%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20a%20terrorist%20in%20need%20of%20legal%20advice%3F%20Better%20call%20Keir%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20mocked-up%20poster%20published%20by%20the%20Conservatives%20this%20week%20on%20X%2C%20the%20social%20media%20site%20formerly%20called%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20%40RishiSunak%20sees%20a%20group%20chanting%20jihad%20on%20our%20streets%2C%20he%20bans%20them.%20Keir%20Starmer%20invoices%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20added%20in%20an%20adjacent%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dig%20related%20to%20advice%20that%20Starmer%20gave%20the%20Islamist%20group%20Hizb%20ut-Tahrir%20in%202008%2C%20when%20the%20organisation%20challenged%20a%20ban%20on%20its%20activities%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20in%20London%20this%20week%20declared%20Hizb%20ut-Tahrir%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20organisation%20and%20banned%20it%20from%20operating%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20said%20during%20the%20weekly%20prime%20minister's%20questions%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20now-proscribed%20group%20had%20once%20been%20%26quot%3Ba%20client%26quot%3B%20of%20Starmer's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Keir%20Starmer%20wasn't%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%2C%20he'd%20be%20representing%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20people%20still%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunak's%20press%20secretary%20told%20reporters%20afterwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Labour%20spokesman%20stressed%20that%20Starmer%20did%20not%20formally%20represent%20Hizb%20ut-Tahrir%2C%20and%20shortly%20afterwards%20became%20the%20chief%20state%20prosecutor%20in%20England%20and%20Wales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nature%20of%20being%20a%20lawyer%20is%20th