ak%20has%20accused%20Starmer%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20toolmaker%20and%20a%20nurse%20who%20ran%20a%20donkey%20sanctuary%2C%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20on%20crime%2C%20soft%20on%20criminals%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20has%20dubbed%20him%20%26quot%3BSir%20Softie%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%20told%20an%20ITV%20documentary%20this%20week%20that%20%26quot%3Bof%20course%26quot%3B%20there%20will%20have%20been%20mistakes%20committed%20during%20his%20tenure%20leading%20the%20CPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20there'll%20be%20no%20smoking%20gun%2C%20no%20skeletons%20in%20the%20closet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20YouGov%20poll%20released%20this%20week%20found%20Labour%2027%20points%20ahead%20of%20the%20Conservatives%2C%20before%20the%20election%2C%20the%20date%20of%20which%20Sunak%20is%20yet%20to%20announce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20put%20the%20ruling%20party%20on%20only%2020-percent%20support%2C%20suggesting%20it%20is%20heading%20for%20a%20landslide%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tories%20have%20presided%20over%20a%20crippling%20cost-of-living%20crisis%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20record%20waiting%20lists%20for%20hospital%20treatment%20and%20served%20up%20five%20prime%20ministers%20since%20the%202016%20Brexit%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cupboard%20is%20bare%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Ford%2C%20a%20political%20scientist%20at%20Manchester%20University%2C%20said%20of%20the%20motivation%20for%20the%20personal%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20haven't%20got%20much%20to%20run%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETim%20Bale%2C%20politics%20professor%20at%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20of%20London%2C%20does%20not%20think%20the%20barbs%20will%20land%20with%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20personal%20stuff%20is%20unlikely%20to%20trump%20the%20bread%20and%20butter%20issues%20that%20are%20killing%20this%20government%2C%20most%20obviously%20the%20state%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20the