thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fanother-african-cheetah-dies-10-deaths-so-far-at-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecaught%20up%20with%20African%20cheetah%20expert%20Adrian%20Tordiffe%20in%20an%20exclusive%20email%20interview%20about%20Project%20Cheetah%20and%20his%20role%20in%20it.%20Tordiffe%2C%20a%20veterinary%20wildlife%20specialist%20currently%20based%20in%20India%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20brought%20in%20the%2012%20cheetahs%20from%20South%20Africa%20in%20February%202023%20and%20was%20listed%20as%20one%20of%20the%20experts%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20January%2016%2C%20African%20cheetah%20Shaurya%20(aka%20Freddie)%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fanother-african-cheetah-dies-10-deaths-so-far-at-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Edied%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kuno%20National%20Park.%20The%20animal%20is%20the%20seventh%20adult%20cheetah%20to%20die%20at%20Kuno.%20As%20a%20veterinary%20wildlife%20specialist%20who%20also%20researches%20on%20cheetah%20health%20and%20conservation%2C%20you%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20brought%20in%20the%2012%20cheetahs%20from%20South%20Africa%20in%20February%202023.%20You%20are%20also%20one%20of%20the%20four%20experts%20listed%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20to%20be%20consulted%20for%20advice%20%E2%80%9Cas%20and%20when%20it%20is%20required%E2%80%9D%20in%20May%202023.%20Were%20you%20informed%20of%20the%20symptoms%20that%20the%20cheetah%20exhibited%2C%20or%20its%20death%2C%20or%20asked%20for%20advice%20on%20this%3F%20If%20not%2C%20when%20did%20you%20receive%20the%20last%20communication%20from%20the%20ground%20team%20in%20India%20about%20the%20cheetahs%E2%80%99%20status%2F%20health%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20was%20not%20contacted%20about%20Shaurya%E2%80%99s%20condition%20at%20any%20time.%20I%20learnt%20about%20his%20death%20via%20the%20online%20news%20reports%20on%20X%20(Twitter).%20I%20have%20not%20received%20any%20direct%20information%20on%20the%20health%20of%20the%20cheetahs%20at%20Kuno%20since%20July%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirect%20communication%20from%20Kuno%20had%20started%20to%20decline%20at%20the%20end%20of%20April%202023%20after%20the%20second%20cheetah%20died.%20The%20last%20information%20I%20received%20directly%20from%20veterinarians%20at%20Kuno%20was%20on%20the%2018th%20of%20July.%20Since%20then%20I%20have%20had%20no%20direct%20contact%20with%20any%20Indian%20officials%20involved%20in%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20said%20that%20you%20have%20not%20received%20any%20communication%20at%20all%20about%20the%20cheetahs%2C%20their%20health%20or%20any%20new%20actions%20to%20be%20taken%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20animals%2C%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20since%20July%202023.%20Do%20you%20know%20why%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20male%20cheetah%20Uday%20shortly%20before%20he%20died%20was%20leaked%20to%20the%20press%20in%20April%202023.%20The%20footage%20had%20been%20shared%20with%20me%20earlier%20that%20day%20and%20I%20think%20they%20suspected%20that%20I%20was%20the%20one%20who%20had%20leaked%20it%20to%20the%20press%20%E2%80%93%20I%20certainly%20did%20not.%20When%20more%20cheetahs%20were%20dying%20and%20very%20little%20information%20was%20being%20shared%20with%20me%2C%20I%20started%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20out%20of%20sheer%20frustration%2C%20trying%20to%20persuade%20the%20authorities%20to%20keep%20me%20involved%20so%20that%20I%20could%20help%20prevent%20more%20deaths.%20Unfortunately%20it%20had%20the%20opposite%20effect.%20Gradually%20they%20ostracised%20me%20from%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20330px)%2085vw%2C%20330px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400.jpeg%20399w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082832%2FOZWQm4dv_400x400-150x150.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693820%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdrian%20Tordiffe.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40AdrianTordiffe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20told%20me%20that%20you%20are%20%E2%80%9Cno%20longer%20involved%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20project%20in%20any%20capacity.%20Why%20is%20that%3F%20Did%20you%20get%20any%20official%20intimation%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20saying%20that%20you%20are%20not%20associated%20with%20the%20project%20or%20are%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20panel%20of%20international%20experts%20who%20have%20to%20be%20approached%20for%20advice%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20a%20decision%20you%20have%20taken%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20communication%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20formal%20communication%20with%20me%20regarding%20my%20involvement%20in%20the%20project.%20I%20have%20written%20to%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Project%20Cheetah%20Steering%20Committee%20hoping%20for%20some%20reconciliation.%20He%20did%20not%20even%20acknowledge%20receipt%20of%20my%20letter.%20It%20seemed%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20to%20pursue%20the%20matter%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Etold%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20July%20last%20year%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20was%20%E2%80%9Cavoidable%E2%80%9D.%20Is%20there%20something%20that%20teams%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20or%20the%20administration%20(the%20forest%20department)%20or%20the%20government%2C%20could%20have%20done%20differently%20to%20avoid%20this%3F%20And%20going%20forward%2C%20are%20these%20still%20aspects%20that%20they%20should%20keep%20in%20mind%20for%20the%20success%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20three-day%20delay%20between%20the%20death%20of%20a%20male%20cheetah%20on%20the%2011th%20of%20July%20and%20the%20following%20death%20on%20the%2014th%20of%20July%20last%20year.%20The%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20that%20first%20animal%20should%20have%20been%20obvious%20even%20before%20any%20post%20mortem%20was%20completed%20as%20the%20neck%20area%20of%20the%20animal%20was%20covered%20in%20maggot-induced%20wounds.%20Authorities%20there%20still%20believed%20that%20the%20male%20cheetah%20had%20died%20due%20to%20wounds%20inflicted%20on%20him%20by%20one%20of%20the%20females.%20If%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20the%20first%20case%20had%20been%20correctly%20diagnosed%2C%20the%20death%20of%20the%20other%20two%20cheetahs%20that%20died%20in%20the%20days%20following%20could%20perhaps%20have%20been%20prevented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20were%20the%20main%20challenges%20you%20faced%20when%20you%20were%20involved%20with%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20main%20problem%20is%20the%20secrecy%2C%20political%20rivalry%20and%20the%20egos%20of%20the%20people%20involved.%20The%20high-profile%20nature%20of%20the%20project%20has%20created%20a%20situation%20where%20certain%20people%20stand%20to%20gain%20significant%20political%20points%20with%20those%20in%20power.%20Scientists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovernment-cuts-short-term-of-biologist-y-v-jhala-who-brough-cheetahs-to-india%5C%22%3Elike%20Professor%20%5BY.V.%5D%20Jhala%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20myself%20were%20sidelined%20for%20wanting%20to%20speak%20the%20truth.%20This%20was%20always%20going%20to%20be%20a%20challenging%20project%20as%20we%20had%20no%20real%20template%20or%20precedent%20to%20work%20from.%20It%20was%20critical%20that%20accurate%20scientific%20data%20was%20collected%20and%20shared%20in%20an%20open%20and%20transparent%20manner%20with%20all%20involved.%20Unfortunately%20that%20did%20not%20happen.%20The%20flow%20of%20information%20is%20now%20tightly%20controlled%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20know%20what%20to%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcheetah-experts-not-in-loop-information-deaths%5C%22%3EInformation%20Blackout%20on%20Cheetahs%E2%80%99%20Health%20and%20Status%20Hurts%20Them%2C%20Some%20Experts%20Say%20Not%20in%20Loop%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eyou%20told%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20cheetah%20deaths%20was%20avoidable%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%93%20specifically%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20even%20issued%20a%20gag%20order%2C%20ordering%20that%20officials%20linked%20to%20the%20project%20not%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%20How%20important%20do%20you%20think%20transparency%20with%20the%20media%2F%20people%20is%2C%20for%20Project%20Cheetah%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScience%20cannot%20advance%20in%20a%20society%20where%20information%20is%20controlled%20by%20those%20in%20power.%20If%20scientists%20are%20silenced%2C%20conspiracy%20theories%20are%20allowed%20to%20thrive%20and%20people%20and%20animals%20end%20up%20suffering%20unnecessarily.%20The%20truth%20is%20the%20truth%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20face%3B%20authorities%20just%20do%20not%20want%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20all%20the%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20would%20you%20say%20the%20main%20challenges%20to%20introducing%20cheetahs%20in%20India%20are%2C%20now%20that%20you%20have%20visited%20the%20area%20(Kuno%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20where%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20ongoing)%2C%20and%20seen%20and%20experienced%20the%20functioning%20of%20Project%20Cheetah%20first%20hand%3F%20How%20can%20we%20improve%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20Kuno%20is%20a%20very%20suitable%20habitat%20for%20cheetahs.%20There%20were%20some%20challenges%20with%20the%20climatic%20conditions%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%20last%20year%2C%20but%20I%20think%20the%20animals%20will%20adapt%20quickly%20to%20those%20conditions%20in%202024%20and%20we%20should%20not%20see%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20same%20problems.%20What%20we%20need%20is%20for%20the%20animals%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20management%20camps%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20why%20this%20has%20not%20been%20done%20yet.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20is%20that%20management%20decisions%20there%20seem%20to%20be%20based%20on%20politics%20rather%20than%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20told%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Findia%2Fproject-cheetah-africa-kuno-deaths-b2376338.html%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20in%20July%20that%20you%20still%20think%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20Project%20Cheetah%20is%20%E2%80%9Cone%20possible%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20cheetah%20population%20that%20is%20otherwise%20globally%20on%20the%20decline%E2%80%9D.%20Do%20you%20still%20subscribe%20to%20this%20view%3F%20If%20you%20do%20why%2C%20and%20if%20you%20do%20not%2C%20why%20not%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%20I%20still%20believe%20that%20to%20be%20the%20case.%20There%20are%20very%20few%20opportunities%20for%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20cheetah%20range%20in%20Africa.%20Most%20cheetah%20populations%20in%20unfenced%20reserves%20in%20Africa%20are%20still%20in%20decline%20due%20to%20depletion%20of%20their%20prey%20base%20and%2For%20direct%20persecution.%20These%20factors%20are%20far%20less%20of%20a%20problem%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20looks%20like%20more%20cheetahs%20are%20likely%20to%20come%20to%20India%3A%20India%20has%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fdec%2F05%2Fmore-cheetahs-may-arrive-in-india---this-time-from-kenya-2638851.html%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Easked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20another%20African%20nation%2C%20this%20time%20Kenya%2C%20for%20more%20cheetahs.%20What%20advice%20would%20you%20offer%20for%20the%20success%20of%20the%20project%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20sure%20that%20Kenya%20has%20a%20growing%20population%20of%20cheetahs%20to%20share%20with%20India.%20But%20my%20advice%20would%20be%20to%20import%20the%20animals%20in%20May%2C%20just%20before%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20The%20animals%20can%20then%20remain%20in%20semi-captivity%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20Any%20parasite%20or%20other%20health%20issues%20can%20be%20closely%20monitored%20and%20dealt%20with.%20The%20animals%20should%20then%20be%20released%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20monsoon%20season%20is%20over.%20It%20would%20also%20be%20wise%20to%20carefully%20select%20individuals%20that%20are%20not%20too%20wild%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20be%20easily%20monitored%20by%20the%20monitoring%20teams%20after%20they%20are%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705805999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21082711%2FF6DODXJacAA5xsc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fexclusive-secrecy-political-rivalry-egos-problems-for-project-cheetah-south-african-expert%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2