%20Babar%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20a%20big%20heart.%20We%20both%20agreed%20there's%20no%20issue%2C%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%20try%2C%20they%20should%20experiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat's%20tough%20is%2C%20when%20you%20break%20things%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20public%20sees%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20was%20going%20well%2C%20but%20the%20management%20was%20trying%20to%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705803720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ffgo68me8_mohammad-amir_625x300_13_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fhad-fun-for-mohammad-aamirs-sly-dig-at-mohammad-rizwan-for-nuksaan-hua-hai-comment-4900677%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammad%20Amir%20took%20a%20sly%20dig%20at%20ex-teammate%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20over%20the%20latter's%20comments%20on%20how%20breaking%20his%20opening%20partnership%20with%20Babar%20Azam%20has%20hurt%20the%20national%20side%20in%20T20Is.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2216%2C000%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20were%20women%20or%20children%3A%20UN%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705803575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107021751%2Cimgsize-1309303.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2F16000-killed-in-gaza-were-women-or-children-un%2Farticleshow%2F107021734.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107021734.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2F16000-killed-in-gaza-were-women-or-children-un%2Farticleshow%2F107021734.cms%22%2