of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Provincial%20Armed%20Constabulary%20(PAC)%20patrolling%20up%20and%20down%20the%20critical%20streets%20of%20this%20temple%20town%20are%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20excitement%20and%20fervour%20that%20is%20all-pervading%20in%20and%20around%20Ayodhya%2C%20where%20all%20roads%20lead%20to%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20that%20is%20to%20be%20pompously%20inaugurated%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEerie%20silence%20seems%20to%20prevail%20particularly%20in%20a%20few%20of%20the%20lanes%20and%20bylanes%2C%20known%20to%20be%20dominated%20by%20Muslims%2C%20who%20are%20stated%20to%20be%20not%20more%20than%205%2C000%20in%20the%20old%20Ayodhya%20town%2C%20among%20the%20four%20lakh%20Muslims%20residing%20in%20the%20entire%20erstwhile%20Faizabad%20district%20(now%20renamed%20Ayodhya).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20appears%20quite%20distinct%20that%20the%20khakhi-clad%20are%20in%20much%20larger%20numbers%20along%20streets%20overlooking%20any%20part%20of%20the%20temple%20construction%20activity.%20One%20such%20locality%20is%20Daurai%20Kuan%20while%20another%20is%20Dharam%20Kanta%20Panjitola%2C%20where%20unusual%20police%20surveillance%20is%20quite%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20explanation%20is%20that%20cops%20in%20these%20localities%20are%20deployed%20simply%20because%20these%20localities%20are%20closer%20to%20the%20outer%20iron%20fencing%20around%20the%20new%20temple.%20However%2C%20residents%20of%20the%20area%20have%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20police%20are%20maintaining%20extra%20surveillance%20because%20of%20the%20larger%20presence%20of%20Muslims%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20allege%20to%20be%20under%20constant%20intimidation%20and%20fear%20of%20losing%20their%20homes%2C%20where%20they%20have%20been%20living%20for%20generations.%20Quite%20a%20few%20of%20them%20had%20moved%20out%20in%20December%201992%2C%20when%20the%2016%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0century%20Ba