.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoyer%2C%20a%20former%20House%20majority%20leader%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marylandmatters.org%2F2022%2F04%2F29%2Fpolitical-notes-hoyer-endorses-wes-moore-for-governor-plus-legislative-candidates-backed-by-casa-in-action-sierra-club%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Moore's%20campaign%20months%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaryland-governor-house-primary-elections-live-results-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20Democratic%20gubernatorial%20primary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20now-governor%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20seized%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20FBI%20issue%20even%20before%20his%20eventual%20win%20in%20the%20primary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20digested%20and%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20our%20competitive%20advantage%20and%20focused%20on%20achieving%20that%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoyer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20recognized%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20FBI%20for%20Maryland%20and%20in%20particular%20for%20Prince%20George's%20County.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20George's%20County%2C%20the%20majority-Black%20county%20directly%20to%20the%20east%20of%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20has%20for%20years%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2022%2F06%2F29%2Fdept-of-data-prince-georges-richest-black-county%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20most%20affluent%20Black%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20any%20jurisdiction%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20compared%20to%20Northern%20Virginia%20localities%20like%20Fairfax%20County%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20economic%20powerhouse%20for%20decades%2C%20Prince%20George's%20County%20hasn't%20enjoyed%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FBI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65abfc99dcdb354a98596d66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20J.%20Edgar%20Hoover%20Building%20in%20downtown%20Washington%20is%20an%20outdated%20facility%20that%20doesn't%20serve%20the%20FBI's%20long-term%20needs.%3Cp%3EERIC%20BARADAT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20new%20building%20%E2%80%94%20which%20will%20consolidate%20and%20hold%20roughly%2011%2C000%20employees%20under%20one%20roof%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%204%25%20of%20leased%20federal%20office%20space%20in%20Prince%20George's%20County%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoyer%20told%20me%2C%20while%20also%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20county%20is%20home%20to%20roughly%2020%25%20of%20the%20Washington%20region's%20federal%20workers.%20%26quot%3BFairfax%20County%20has%2011%25%20of%20the%20office%20space%2C%20almost%20three%20times%20as%20much%20as%20we%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoyer%2C%20like%20Moore%2C%20argued%20during%20the%20selection%20process%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2023%2F03%2F08%2Ffbi-headquarters-wes-moore-maryland%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Maryland%20site%20would%20be%20tied%20to%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20race%20but%20also%20regarding%20the%20level%20of%20federal%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20project%20will%20be%20worth%20over%20%244%20billion%20in%20economic%20activity%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20solidify%20Maryland%20as%20the%20cyber%20capital%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20told%20me%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20that%20we%20made%20it%20such%20a%20high%20priority%20is%20because%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20federal%20buildings%20that%20has%20ever%20been%20built.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirginia%20leaders%2C%20who%20for%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2023%2F06%2F08%2Ffbi-headquarters-maryland-virginia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20suburban%20site%20near%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20Base%20Quantico%20was%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20the%20headquarters%2C%20have%20criticized%20the%20selection%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20the%20General%20Service%20Administration%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffbi-headquarters-investigation-virginia-maryland-9c923cd2909eb3597708d498c859f44b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econduct%20an%20evaluation%20of%20the%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbeyer.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fdocumentsingle.aspx%3FDocumentID%3D6028%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20November%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20Virginia's%20congressional%20delegation%20asked%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20move%20the%20headquarters%20to%20the%2061-acre%20Greenbelt%20site%20be%20reversed.%20And%20current%20FBI%20director%20Christopher%20Wray%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Ffbi-director-virginia-relocate-fbi-hq-maryland-00126444%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpressed%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20in%20November%20defended%20the%20selection%20process%20as%20%26quot%3Bfair%20and%20transparent.%26quot%3B%20And%20Maryland's%20leaders%20remain%20confident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20absolutely%20convinced%20that%20everything%20was%20done%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoyer%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I've%20been%20convinced%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20that%20Greenbelt%20was%20by%20far%20the%20best%20site%20for%20all%20the%20reasons%20that%20the%20GSA%20ultimately%20found.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid