or%20Two-State%20Solution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20210122%2FEffect-77.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20their%20first%20meeting%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20Indian%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%20discussed%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20foreign%20minister%20Riyad%20al-Maliki%20and%20reaffirmed%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20ministers%20met%20in%20the%20Ugandan%20capital%20Kampala%20on%20Saturday%2C%20where%20both%20sides%20are%20attending%20the%20summit%20of%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20his%20official%20account%20on%20X%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdetailed%20and%20comprehensive%20discussion%20on%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D%20with%20Al-Maliki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20they%20exchanged%20views%20on%20its%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20and%20political%20dimensions%E2%80%9D%2C%20Jaishankar%20wrote%20that%20he%20also%20%E2%80%9Creiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGood%20to%20meet%20with%20Palestinian%20FM%20Dr.%20Riyad%20al-Maliki%20in%20Kampala%20this%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20a%20detailed%20and%20comprehensive%20discussion%20on%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Gaza.%20Exchanged%20views%20on%20its%20humanitarian%20and%20political%20dimensions.%20Reiterated%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9GJNzPqqfg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F9GJNzPqqfg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1748650520468721784%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20refers%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20independent%20Palestinian%20state%20along%20Israel%20within%20secure%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20with%20Palestine%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Jaishankar%20attempted%20to%20balance%20India%E2%80%99s%20unconditional%20condemnation%20of%20Hamas%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20with%20a%20reiteration%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20at%20the%20NAM%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20also%20be%20clear%20that%20terrorism%20and%20hostage-taking%20are%20unacceptable.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20must%20always%20be%20respected%20by%20all%20States.%20It%20is%20also%20imperative%20that%20conflict%20does%20not%20spread%20within%20or%20beyond%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%20Palestinian%20Islamist%20group%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20an%20attack%20from%20Gaza%20into%20southern%20Israel%20which%20killed%20over%201200%20people%20and%20took%20around%20240%20as%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20counterattack%20on%20Gaza%2C%20which%20included%20airstrikes%20and%20ground%20invasion%2C%20more%20than%2024%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%20population%20facing%20chronic%20shortages%20of%20all%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20water%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20medical%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%E2%80%99%20with%20Israel.%20India%20started%20to%20nuance%20its%20position%20about%20a%20week%20later%20following%20the%20attack%20on%20a%20big%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20by%20referring%20to%20its%20principled%20traditional%20support%20for%20Palestine.%20However%2C%20India%20was%20still%20among%20the%20handful%20of%20developing%20countries%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20first%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20on%20the%20conflict%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-votes-in-favour-of-unga-resolution-calling-for-immediate-ceasefire-in-gaza%5C%22%3EIndia%20voted%20in%20favour%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20second%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20that%20called%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20remains%20among%20few%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20south%20which%20still%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20explicitly%20called%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20its%20national%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20apparent%20at%20Kampala%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F37521%2FIndias%2BNational%2BStatement%2Bby%2BEAM%2BDr%2BS%2BJaishankar%2Bat%2Bthe%2B19th%2BNAM%2BSummit%2Bin%2BKampala%5C%22%3EJaishankar%E2%80%99s%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20no%20mention%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20at%20the%20Gaza%20war%2C%20while%20this%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fnon-aligned-movement-leaders-denounce-israels-military-campaign-gaza-2024-01-19%2F%5C%22%3Edemand%20made%20by%20most%20speakers%20at%20the%20NAM%20summit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpmofa%2Fstatus%2F1748662702216523878%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20summit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20foreign%20minister%20had%20asked%20the%20120-member%20bloc%20to%20%E2%80%9Chalt%20the%20genocide%20and%20achieve%20justice%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%9D.%20He%