A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fjk-cement-q3-net-profit-rises-multi-fold-to-rs-283-81-cr-revenue-up-20-124012000473_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Ayodhya%2C%20Firm%20Linked%20to%20BJP%20Leaders%20Sold%20Ecologically%20Sensitive%20Land%20to%20Adani%20at%20a%20Profit%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Just%20days%20before%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1062426%2Fin-ayodhya-firm-linked-to-bjp-leaders-sold-ecologically-sensitive-land-to-adani-for-a-big-profit%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20its%20detailed%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20found%20out%20about%20land%20dealings%20between%20local%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leaders%20and%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20story%20by%20reporter%20Ayush%20Tiwari%2C%20between%20October%20and%20December%202023%2C%20a%20firm%20called%20Time%20City%20Multi%20State%20Cooperative%20Housing%20Society%20bought%20a%20small%20parcel%20of%20land%20near%20the%20Saryu%20river%20for%20Rs%201.13%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeeks%20later%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20the%20land%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20for%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20price%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%203.57%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20City%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Time%20City%20group%20founded%20by%20Chandra%20Prakash%20Shukla%2C%20a%20former%20chartered%20accountant%20with%20the%20Sahara%20group%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20was%20an%20MLA%20from%20Kaptanganj%20between%202017%20and%202022.%20The%20group%20is%20run%20by%20Shukla%E2%80%99s%20former%20business%20associate%2C%20Pankaj%20Pathak%20%E2%80%93%20a%20BJP%20member%2C%20who%20the%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20says%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20friends%20in%20the%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP%20party%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20deal%2C%20it%20was%20the%20farmers%20who%20sold%20the%20land%20for%20a%20cheap%20throwaway%20price.%20The%20land%20deal%20also%20raises%20many%20ecological%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20Time%20City%20bought%20a%20hectare%20of%20land%20in%20Majha%20Jamthara.%20That%20land%20belonged%20to%20the%20families%20of%20Ghanseera%20Yadav%20and%20Kabootra%20Devi%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20in%20Majha%20Jamthara%20that%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20is%20part%20of%20the%20environmentally%20sensitive%20wetland%20near%20Saryu%2C%20a%20habitat%20of%20the%20Sarus%20crane%2C%20grey%20heron%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20fox.%20Since%20December%202022%2C%20the%20government%20has%20prohibited%20any%20new%20construction%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajha%20Jamthara%20is%20a%20vast%2C%20unpopulated%20region%20between%20Faizabad%2C%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20Saryu%20river%20%E2%80%93%20about%205%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20Ram%20temple%20being%20built%20on%20the%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EScroll%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20questions%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Adani%20group%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20transaction%20carried%20out%20by%20%5Bone%20of%20its%20subsidiaries%5D%20is%20completely%20legal%20and%20has%20been%20conducted%20in%20accordance%20with%20all%20laws%20and%20regulations.%20The%20company%20acquired%20land%20at%20the%20prevailing%20circle%20rates.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EScroll%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20investigation%20has%20further%20found%20that%20in%20February%202021%2C%20the%20Yadavs%20sold%200.56%20hectares%20of%20the%20land%20they%20had%20inherited%20to%20Sudha%20Dixit%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kanpur%2C%20for%20Rs%2033.53%20lakh%20over%20two%20transactions.%20This%20amount%20is%20significantly%20below%20the%20land%E2%80%99s%20circle%20rate%20(minimum)%20price%2C%20which%20the%20report%20claims%20then%20stood%20at%20Rs%2077.46%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20common%20witness%20in%20both%20these%20transactions%20was%20Suryabhan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20legal%20advisor%20to%20Time%20City%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20expose%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20Dixit%20sold%20this%20property%20to%20Time%20City%20for%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20over%20two%20sale%20deeds%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20two%20separate%20transactions.%20The%20witnesses%20in%20both%20the%20sale%20deeds%20were%20Jaibhan%20Singh%20and%20Avinash%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Yadavs%20sold%20another%20land%20parcel%20of%200.44%20hectare%20directly%20Time%20City%20for%20Rs%2033%20lakh.%20This%20time%20too%20the%20deal%20was%20much%20below%20the%20circle%20price%20and%C2%A0%C2%A0the%20witnesses%20in%20the%20deal%20were%20Avinash%20Singh%20and%20Sitaram%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20all%20witnesses%20in%20these%20three%20transactions%20are%20linked%20to%20local%20BJP%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryabhan%20and%20Jaibhan%20are%20brothers%20of%20Chandrabhan%20Singh%2C%20a%20BJP%20worker%20and%20member%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20zila%20panchayat.%20Avinash%20is%20Chandrabhan%E2%80%99s%20son.%20Sitaram%20Yadav%20is%20the%20father-in-law%20of%20Suman%20Yadav%2C%20a%20BJP%20municipal%20councillor%20from%20Amaniganj%20in%20Faizabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20transaction%2C%20the%20other%20aspect%20that%20has%20come%20under%20a%20scanner%20is%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20sale%20of%20land%20to%20a%20private%20player%20in%20an%20ecologically%20sensitive%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EScroll%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20highlights%20the%202019%20committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%