0City%20of%20India%2C%20is%20known%20in%20the%20country%20for%20being%20the%20largest%20producer%20of%20mushrooms%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20delicious%20fungi%20and%20beautiful%20landscapes%2C%20the%20place%20is%20also%20becoming%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20innovation.%20While%20most%20of%20the%20youth%20shy%20away%20from%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20considering%20it%20low%20in%20profits%20%E2%80%94%20Gaurav%20Sabharwal%20is%20changing%20the%20narrative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20that%20many%20people%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20farming%20is%20not%20profitable%20but%20it%20depends%20on%20what%20you%20are%20growing.%20While%20most%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20city%20are%20into%20mushroom%20farming%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20new%20to%20make%20it%20more%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%20is%20growing%20saffron%20using%20aeroponics%20in%20his%20300%20sq%20ft%20setup%20in%20Solan.%20With%20a%20controlled%20environment%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327439%2Fnagaland-woman-lhuvevolu-rhakho-grows-shiitake-mushrooms-on-oak-logs-native-organics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20chemical-free%20%3C%2Fa%3Eenvironment%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20grow%20500%20gm%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98red%20gold%E2%80%99%20and%20sell%20it%20at%20a%20remarkable%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20know%20how%20he%20grew%20Saffron%20that%20can%20only%20be%20grown%20in%20Kashmir%3F%20Here%20is%20his%20story%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Adversity%20leads%20to%20innovation%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Solan%2C%20Gaurav%20aspired%20to%20follow%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20sm