g%20the%20loan%2C%20Gaurav%20worked%20diligently%20to%20make%20his%20family%20business%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCall%20it%20fate%2C%20but%20the%20business%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20yielding%20much%20profit%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20pressure%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20began%20exploring%20avenues%20for%20more%20lucrative%20ventures.%20One%20thing%20I%20was%20clear%20about%20%E2%80%93%20I%20wanted%20to%20run%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20numerous%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20planters%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Solan%20who%20were%20earning%20substantial%20incomes.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20market%20saturated%20with%20producers%2C%20prices%20were%20steadily%20decreasing.%20I%20realised%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20something%20different.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20options%20online%20is%20when%20he%20found%20out%20about%20the%20precious%20%E2%80%98red%20gold%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20saffron.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20knows%20how%20expensive%20saffron%20is%20and%20how%20profitable%20it%20can%20be.%20However%2C%20I%20always%20assumed%20that%20it%20can%20only%20be%20grown%20in%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20started%20researching%20on%20the%20internet%20if%20there%20were%20ways%20of%20growing%20it%20in%20Himachal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20internet%20has%20all%20the%20answers%20and%20that%20is%20how%20I%20found%20out%20about%20the%20technique%20of%20using%20a%20controlled%20environment%20for%20growing%20different%20types%20of%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20a%20few%20instances%20where%20people%20grew%20saffron%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337129%2Feroponics-tower-planter-for-balcony-garden-by-iit-kanpur-startup-macrogardens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20aeroponics.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Aeroponics%20is%20a%20way%20of%20growing%20plants%20without%20soil.%20Instead%20of%20planting%20them%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20plants%20hang%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20their%20roots%20are%20misted%20with%20a%20nutrient-rich%20spray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAeroponics%20can%20help%20plants%20grow%20faster%2C%20use%20less%20water%2C%20and%20be%20more%20resistant%20to%20certain%20diseases%20compared%20to%20traditional%20soil-based%20methods.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20giving%20plants%20a%20shower%20of%20nutrients%20to%20help%20them%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20heart%20set%20on%20growing%20saffron%2C%20he%20set%20on%20a%20journey%20of%20learning%20aeroponics%20from%20scratch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20profits%20and%20teaching%20others%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-5-1705413070.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20named%20his%20saffron%20farm%20after%20his%20mother.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-5-1705413070.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-5-1705413070-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-5-1705413070-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-5-1705413070-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-5-1705413070-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338360%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurav%20named%20his%20saffron%20farm%20after%20his%20mother.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Gaurav%20Sabharwal%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20the%20first%20thing%20that%20most%20people%20would%20do%20%E2%80%94%20go%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20read%20up%20about%20aeroponics.%20I%20found%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20growing%20saffron%20using%20the%20technique%2C%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20contact%20them%2C%20reaching%20out%20for%20their%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20research%20that%20he%20found%20out%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20he%20would%20need%20to%20set%20up%20his%20farm%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20investment%2C%20so%20I%20sought%20help%20from%20the%20government.%20I%20got%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20even%20got%20a%20rebate%20under%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20startup%20scheme%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20right%20investment%20in%20hand%2C%20Gaurav%20was%20ready%20to%20try%20his%20hand%20at%20growing%20saffron%20in%20Solan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20greatest%20factor%20to%20consider%20was%20that%20the%20temperature%20needed%20to%20grow%20saffron%20was%20only%20in%20Kashmir%20in%20India.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20mimic%20that%20here%20in%20Solan.%20I%20used%20the%20lab%20whose%20temperature%20can%20be%20controlled%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20mimicking%20the%20environment%20and%20planting%20the%20seeds%2C%20it%20was%20important%20for%20me%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20buds.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20that%20they%20can%20catch%20fungus%20and%20was%20taken%20aback%20when%20my%20first%20crop%20did%20catch%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20able%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it%20by%20drying%20the%20affected%20plants%20and%20separating%20them%20from%20the%20healthy%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%208%20months%20of%20hard%20labour%20and%20planning%2C%20Gaurav%20was%20able%20to%20grow%20500%20grams%20of%20saffron%20in%20his%20aeroponics%20farm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20produce%2C%20although%20not%20a%20lot%2C%20was%20a%20good%20sign.%20I%20was%20very%20tense%20because%20this%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20me.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20had%20no%20intentions%20of%20doing%20anything%20and%20seeing%20those%20buds%20flower%20was%20a%20great%20feeling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20sold%20his%20first%20produce%20at%20a%20price%20of%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-6-1705413451-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338363%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurav%20sold%20his%20first%20produce%20for%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Gaurav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20ready%20with%20his%20produce%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20it%20at%20Rs%20500%20per%20gram.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20market%20rate%20was%20Rs%20300%20but%20those%20are%20not%20